    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/abecf938f13a330d76b03cb451e1e15d.avif?t=1755065679\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/6a7acc9e48a04061ea4f5fc5951d20de.poster.avif?t=1755065679\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/6a7acc9e48a04061ea4f5fc5951d20de.webm?t=1755065679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/6a7acc9e48a04061ea4f5fc5951d20de.mp4?t=1755065679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《天命奇御：归途》是一款含有Roguelite随机要素的动作角色扮演游戏。你将扮演主人翁诸葛羽，因一场意外，遭受重创陷入昏迷，醒来之后发现自己来到了一个陌生的地方，通过神秘力量的指引，逐渐找回丧失的过往记忆。在一路过关斩将的过程中，不断收集天赋、获取信物、搭配招式，形成独特的战斗流派，体验不同的关卡路线和战斗节奏，最终击败环伺的强敌，寻回失去的记忆，并踏上回归的旅途。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/a32a387e8d394009f1d44f6dd7c716c5.avif?t=1755065679\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/c54826fa55a9f996ae25c2e6a3138bd6.poster.avif?t=1755065679\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/c54826fa55a9f996ae25c2e6a3138bd6.webm?t=1755065679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/c54826fa55a9f996ae25c2e6a3138bd6.mp4?t=1755065679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> 一股神秘力量指引着诸葛羽前进，进入每一座关卡之前，都要面对未知的抉择：是选择找回记忆的碎片？抑或是选择增强实力手刃强敌？而在每次进入关卡、结束战斗之后，抉择的天赋和收集的信物，都将成为你最终击倒强敌、找回遗失记忆的助力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/7f02e18f9b0991b611f3ca479fe4fedf.avif?t=1755065679\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/d75fb96d4fddeeeb963589a229c7c358.poster.avif?t=1755065679\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/d75fb96d4fddeeeb963589a229c7c358.webm?t=1755065679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/d75fb96d4fddeeeb963589a229c7c358.mp4?t=1755065679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在与迥异的敌人进行对决时，你需要掌握出招与闪避的时机，配合获得的随机招式与天赋，从而赢得战斗的胜利。值得一提的是，一些特定的天赋除了能够提升角色的战斗能力之外，还能为刀枪剑戟等武器装备增加炫丽的外观特效，带来强烈的视觉效果与爽快十足的战斗打击体验！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/e38f5527fc2ffdc7064fb4c8ae7aa3e2.avif?t=1755065679\" width=616 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/ca2a33541dee2a0ec62a8436023e95d7.poster.avif?t=1755065679\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/ca2a33541dee2a0ec62a8436023e95d7.webm?t=1755065679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/ca2a33541dee2a0ec62a8436023e95d7.mp4?t=1755065679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>过五关，斩六将！身为诸葛羽的你经过层层试炼，历经艰险，终于击败了来犯的强敌。在不断战斗的过程中，过往遗失的记忆被逐渐寻回，但随之而来的却是令人措手不及的沉重真相，你只能勇往直前，一次又一次地踏上扭转乾坤的旅程......<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关注最新消息</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2124420/extras/9ffe07dfef426a94cfe8105a05202b4a.avif?t=1755065679\" width=616 height=160 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>《天命奇御：归途》官方1群：721141794（可加）</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>《天命奇御》系列官方1群：775653305（可加）</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>《天命奇御二》官方4群：767896075（可加）</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>《天命奇御二》官方3群：248285298（已满）</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>《天命奇御二》官方2群：793464907 (已满)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >联系我们</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>凤凰客服QQ：4000722815</li></ul>随时提出您的建议和回馈，我们将竭诚为您服务。",
